    "The choice of DW can affect global transport characteristics, as well as the Luttinger parameters of the 1D chiral/helical modes (if they remain ungapped).",
    "Numerical Particularities One-dimensional Translational Symmetry BreakingFor the numerical calculations (see Fig. 9a for an illustration of the setup), we assume the usual periodic boundary conditions with N 1, N 2 moiré unit cells along the a 1, a 2 directions respectively.",
